(29, 9, 1, '', '2016-09-17 07:53:56', 748, 16045, '7cf00d54ca555da96e67a0e966d7c123b0b6bff3', '{"id":9,"asset_id":131,"title":"In UV Pet d\\u1ebbo ","alias":"in-uv-pet-deo","introtext":"<div class=\\"post-info-description\\" style=\\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid transparent;\\">C&ocirc;ng ty In K\\u1ef9 Thu\\u1eadt S\\u1ed1 chuy&ecirc;n cung c\\u1ea5p c&aacute;c g&oacute;i d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 In UV Pet d\\u1ebbo (PVC sim) ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao d&ugrave;ng in h\\u1ed9p m\\u1ef9 ph\\u1ea9m, h\\u1ed9p \\u0111\\u1ef1ng qu&agrave; t\\u1eb7ng, h\\u1ed9p trong su\\u1ed1t \\u0111\\u1ef1ng \\u0111\\u1ed3,... v\\u1edbi gi&aacute; r\\u1ebb nh\\u1ea5t th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i t\\u1ef1 h&agrave;o l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng ty in \\u1ea5n uy t&iacute;n tr&ecirc;n 10 n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong ngh\\u1ec1, mang l\\u1ea1i cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m tuy\\u1ec7t h\\u1ea3o.<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"congso-post\\" style=\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; border: 0px solid transparent;\\">\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit;\\">In UV Pet d\\u1ebbo (PVC sim) l&agrave; g&igrave;?<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; text-align: justify;\\">PET(Polyethylene terephthalate)&nbsp;l&agrave; m\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng ch\\u1ea5t d\\u1ebbo th\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng trong c&aacute;c s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng, v&agrave; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t&igrave;m th\\u1ea5y trong h\\u1ea7u h\\u1ebft c&aacute;c chai n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v&agrave; pop, v&agrave; m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 bao b&igrave;. N&oacute; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c&nbsp;