(37, 8, 1, '', '2016-09-17 08:31:59', 748, 13882, '62f0c359139975045ccb97310047ce7f64c29362', '{"id":8,"asset_id":"130","title":"In UV canvas m\\u1edd","alias":"in-uv-canvas-mo","introtext":"<div>C&ocirc;ng ty In K\\u1ef9 Thu\\u1eadt S\\u1ed1 chuy&ecirc;n cung c\\u1ea5p d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 in uv canvas m\\u1edd d&ugrave;ng trang tr&iacute; n\\u1ed9i ngo\\u1ea1i th\\u1ea5t nh&agrave; \\u1edf, v\\u0103n ph&ograve;ng l&agrave;m vi\\u1ec7c, ... v\\u1edbi ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao, gi&aacute; th&agrave;nh r\\u1ebb v&agrave; giao h&agrave;ng \\u0111&uacute;ng h\\u1eb9n v\\u1edbi kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng<br \\/>","fulltext":"<\\/div>\\r\\n<div>\\r\\n<p>In UV Canvas m\\u1edd l&agrave; g&igrave;?<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Canvas (v\\u1ea3i b\\u1ed1) l&agrave; lo\\u1ea1i ch\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec7u v\\u1ea3i cao c\\u1ea5p, canvas c&oacute; b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t gi\\u1ed1ng v\\u1ea3i, do b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t c&oacute; d\\u1ea1ng l\\u01b0\\u1edbi n&ecirc;n canvas th\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 in c&aacute;c b\\u1ee9c tranh m\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>In Canvas c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 b\\u1eb1ng m\\u1ef1c n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ho\\u1eb7c m\\u1ef1c d\\u1ea7u, tu\\u1ef3 v&agrave;o m\\u1ee5c \\u0111&iacute;ch s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng m&agrave; b\\u1ea1n l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn lo\\u1ea1i m\\u1ef1c in. C\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3, n\\u1ebfu b\\u1ea1n mu\\u1ed1n tr\\u01b0ng b&agrave;y trong nh&agrave; th&igrave; d&ugrave;ng m\\u1ef1c n\\u01b0\\u1edbc, ng\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u1ea1i \\u1edf ngo&agrave;i tr\\u1eddi th&igrave; d&ugrave;ng m\\u1ef1c d\\u1ea7u.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>In UV Canvas m\\u1edd v\\u1edbi c&ocirc;ng ngh\\u1ec7 in UV b\\u1eb1ng m&aacute;y in UV hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i t\\u1ea1i C&ocirc;ng ty In K\\u1ef9 Thu\\u1eadt S\\u1ed1, s\\u1ebd kh&ocirc;ng kh&oacute; \\u0111\\u1ec3 c&oacute; cho b\\u1ea1n m\\u1ed9t tuy\\u1ec7t t&aacute;c h\\u1ed9i h\\u1ecda \\u0111\\u1ec3 tr\\u01b0ng b&agrave;y trong nh&agrave;. N\\u1ebfu b\\u1ea1n th&iacute;ch b\\u1ee9c tranh \\u0111\\u1ec3 trang tr&iacute; trong ph&ograve;ng b\\u1ea1n, b\\u1ea1n ch\\u1ec9 c\\u1ea7n ch\\u1edd &iacute;t nh\\u1ea5t 60 ph&uacute;t s\\u1ebd c&oacute; ngay m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ee9c tranh \\u0111&uacute;ng nh\\u01b0 &yacute; v\\u1edbi c&ocirc;ng ngh\\u1ec7 in Canvas ho&agrave;n h\\u1ea3o.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/cdn.inkythuatso.com\\/asset\\/home\\/img\\/500\\/579c33b462df2_1469854644.jpg\\" alt=\\"In uv canvas c&aacute;n m\\u1edd\\" width=\\"500\\" height=\\"375\\" style=\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\" title=\\"In uv canvas c&aacute;n m\\u1edd\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>In uv silk, in uv canvas c&aacute;n m\\u1edd l&agrave;m tranh \\u1ea3nh c&oacute; ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng cao. S\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m in b\\u1eb1ng m\\u1ef1c d\\u1ea7u c&oacute; \\u0111\\u1ed9 b\\u1ec1n m&agrave;u l&acirc;u d&agrave;i<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>S\\u1ef1 kh&aacute;c bi\\u1ec7t c\\u1ee7a&nbsp;<a href=\\"http:\\/\\/inkythuatso.com\\/bang-bao-gia-in-uv-808.html\\" target=\\"_blank\\" title=\\"in canvas m\\u1edd b\\u1eb1ng c&ocirc;ng ngh\\u1ec7 In UV\\">in canvas m\\u1edd b\\u1eb1ng c&ocirc;ng ngh\\u1ec7 In UV<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>In tranh \\u1ea3nh trang tr&iacute; b\\u1eb1ng c&ocirc;ng ngh\\u1ec7 in th\\u01b0\\u1eddng:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>M&agrave;u nhanh tr&ocirc;i<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>\\u0110\\u1ed9 b\\u1ec1n th\\u1ea5p<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng th\\u1ea5p<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>In qu\\u1ea3ng c&aacute;o, trang tr&iacute; v\\u1edbi v\\u1ea3i canvas b\\u1eb1ng c&ocirc;ng ngh\\u1ec7 in uv:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Canvas c&ograve;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c g\\u1ecdi l&agrave; v\\u1ea3i b\\u1ed1, Canvas l&agrave; m\\u1ed9t lo\\u1ea1i v\\u1ea3i cao c\\u1ea5p, b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t ch\\u1ea5t li\\u1ec7u d\\u1ea1ng l\\u01b0\\u1edbi c&aacute;c s\\u1edbi v\\u1ea3i \\u0111an xen v\\u1edbi nhau t\\u1ea1o th&agrave;nh m\\u1ed9t m\\u1ea3ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng nh\\u1ea5t, b\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t d\\u1ea1ng l\\u01b0\\u1edbi n&ecirc;n khi s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n c&aacute;c b\\u1ee9c \\u1ea3nh ngh\\u1ec7 thu\\u1eadt s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 cao nh\\u1ea5t. B\\u1ec1 m\\u1eb7t Canvas \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u1ee7 m\\u1ed9t l\\u1edbp nh\\u1ef1a d&ugrave;ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 gi\\u1eef m\\u1ef1c l\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ea3m \\u0111\\u1ed9 th\\u1ea5m m\\u1ef1c v&agrave;o s\\u1ee3i v\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1ec3 gi\\u1eef \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c m&agrave;u s\\u1eafc trung th\\u1ef1c h\\u01a1n.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Khung tranh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t&ugrave;y ch\\u1ecdn th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ed9 d&agrave;y m&agrave; b\\u1ea1n mong mu\\u1ed1n, th&iacute;ch h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi v\\u1ecb tr&iacute; treo tranh trong kh&ocirc;ng gian nh&agrave; b\\u1ea1n.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt in ng\\u01b0\\u1ee3c &ndash; nh\\u1edd v&agrave;o \\u01b0u \\u0111i\\u1ec3m d\\u1ec5 d&agrave;ng h&uacute;t m\\u1ef1c, t\\u1ee9c m\\u1ef1c s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c in \\u1edf m\\u1eb7t sau c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ee9c tranh, sau \\u0111&oacute; s\\u1ebd th\\u1ea9m th\\u1ea5u ra m\\u1eb7t tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc, cho h&igrave;nh \\u1ea3nh \\u0111\\u1eb9p m\\u1ecbn v&agrave; \\u0111\\u1ec1u h\\u01a1n.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>H&igrave;nh \\u1ea3nh \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o 100% s\\u1ef1 h&agrave;i l&ograve;ng.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n in tranh canvas \\u0111&oacute;n ch&agrave;o nh\\u1eefng v\\u1ecb kh&aacute;ch gh&eacute; th\\u0103m kh&ocirc;ng gian ri&ecirc;ng c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>H&igrave;nh \\u1ea3nh tranh canvas \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c in tr&ecirc;n v\\u1ea3i chuy&ecirc;n d\\u1ee5ng, c&oacute; ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v\\u1edbi v\\u1ea3i m\\u1ef9 thu\